sentence.text: In 128 female patients of the recruited UCC cohort, patients who carried at least one deletion allele of adenylate cyclase-inhibiting dopamine receptor signaling pathway rs1799732 showed a higher incidence of having an invasive stage (AOR=2.585, 95% CI: 1.066~6.264, p=0.032) and a large tumor (AOR=2.778, 95% CI: 1.146~6.735, p=0.021).

sentence.text: Further analyses of The Cancer Genome Atlas (TCGA) and Gene Expression Omnibus (GEO) datasets revealed correlations of the expression of adenylate cyclase-inhibiting dopamine receptor signaling pathway with an invasive tumor, tumor metastasis, and the lower survival rate in patients with UCC.
